<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA53">
<l>muyaṉṟu toḻuneñcē mūrinīr vēlai</l>
<l>yiyaṉṟamarat tālilaiyiṉ mēlāṟ – payiṉṟaṅkōr</l>
<l>maṇṇalaṅkoḷ veḷḷattu māyak kuḻaviyāy</l>
<l>taṇṇalaṅkaṉ mālaiyāṉ ṟāḷ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Diligently worship, heart – the feet of him with a cool swaying garland,</l>
<l>as a miraculous child in the flood that had taken the goodness</l>
<l>of the one earth, abiding there by the banyan , on the banyan leaf of a tree</l>
<l>that moved forward in the ancient water, the ocean.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
